# LasallEats ğŸ½ï¸
An emotion-based food recommender built with Streamlit.

Note:
Before using the application, please get your own Gemini API key

## ğŸ› ï¸ Setup

# (Optional) Create and activate virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # or venv\Scripts\activate on Windows

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Setup secrets

1. Make a directory named ".streamlit"
mkdir -p .streamlit
nano .streamlit/secrets.toml

2. Add this inside the secrets.toml file
[api_keys]
gemini = "YOUR API KEY HERE"

# Run the app
1. Run this in your terminal
streamlit run main.py
